# .llmignore - Generated at rival.tips/llmignore
# Files and patterns AI agents should never read or send to LLMs.
# Syntax: identical to .gitignore (fnmatch patterns)

# Secrets & credentials
.env
.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/credentials.*
**/secrets.*
**/.secret*

# Sensitive data
**/migrations/*.sql
**/fixtures/**
**/seed-data/**

# Large binaries
**/*.wasm
**/*.bin
**/*.sqlite
**/*.db

# Dependency Lockfiles
**/go.sum

# Vendor directories
**/vendor/**

# Large test fixtures
testdata/
*_test.json
*.golden

# Pre-compiled or generated assets
mocks/
*_mock.go
